e":"2017-04-25T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"咁女廁冇尿兜一定係殘障岐視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc1bbdf1bb9d471edf172d330275245dcf4fe7f","tid":215550,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身預係複式單位再改建？</blockquote><br />\n可能係部lift頂機位</blockquote><br />\n在商言商，可以話佢當初係想賺多啲<br />\n但呢種起法亦可能係因為當年因啟德機場，樓宇有高度限制<br />\n九龍有唔少住宅樓宇都係咁<br />\n其實買入單位嗰時應該清楚有咁嘅設計，而家先攞嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法例咁寫就咁寫，你賣埋頂樓係你on9"},{"pid":"1bf5fbfc767840798b2dc01a8e0cfcd8867f0969","tid":215550,"uid":56501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"唐樓點計？"},{"pid":"0a8f5e9052f6a821169c15cc70643c8f89c37630","tid":215550,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唐樓點計？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全部都行樓梯=公平"}]}